Last Broadcast Date: Wed 3 Aug 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world: today, the bereaved mother who has dedicated her life to helping the families of those disappeared by the IRA. Also the prisoner in a Bangladesh jail who was asked to become an executioner. And the holy month at high speed - we join two men doing a Ramadan road trip across the USA. Show less